; ARRAYS: FIXED-SIZE, VALUE TYPES (NO DECAY TO POINTERS).
; THE SUBSCRIPT IS POSTFIX: `BUF I [` IS BUF[I], USABLE FOR READING OR WRITING.

!MAIN W
    !BUF A 3 W
    !I W
    !SUM W
    0 I!
    I 3 < &
        I 10 *  BUF I [ !      ; BUF[I] = I * 10
        I 1 + I!
    0 SUM!
    0 I!
    I 3 < &
        BUF I [  SUM +  SUM!   ; SUM = SUM + BUF[I]
        I 1 + I!
    SUM PRINT                  ; 0 + 10 + 20 = 30
